comments: King (SAC) legally contests Frazier's (MEM) jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Frazier's right foot as he returns to the floor.
Tillman (MEM) has his left hand extended forward and marginal contact occurs with James' (SAC) right arm before Tillman cleanly blocks the shot attempt thereafter.
Tillman (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Ramsey's (SAC) path and turns slightly before absorbing the contact.
Davis (SAC) extends his hands forward and marginal contact occurs with Tillie's (MEM) front during the drive.
Jones (SAC) brings his arm down and initiates contact with Tillie's (MEM) left arm during his upward shooting motion.
Jones (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Tillman's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact. Jones and Tillman then engage and disengage as they move toward the lane.
Davis (SAC) moves forward toward Tillie (MEM) and marginal contact occurs with Tillie's back and right arm as he makes the pass.
Frazier (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in King's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact.

King (SAC) has his right hand slightly extended forward as he turns alongside Frazier's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs during Frazier's drive into the lane. Jones (SAC) then brushes Frazier's front and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Tillman (MEM) engages and disengages with King (SAC) during the inbound.

Frazier (MEM) swipes forward and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Ramsey's (SAC) front after his gather. Porter (MEM) jumps vertically and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs with Ramsey during the follow-through of his shot attempt.
James (SAC) commits a take foul on Tillman (MEM).
Porter (MEM) has his hands slightly extended forward and marginal contact occurs with James' (SAC) front as he is gathering the ball.
Frazier (MEM) and Ramsey (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Ramsey (SAC) initiates arm contact with Frazier (MEM) that affects his SQBR as he dribbles along the sideline.
Frazier (MEM) moves slightly forward toward James (SAC) and marginal contact occurs with James' front before he loses control of the ball.
James (SAC) commits a take foul on Frazier (MEM).
Tillman (MEM) moves forward toward King (SAC) and marginal contact occurs with King's side as he receives the pass.
James (SAC) commits a take foul on Winslow (MEM).
Frazier (MEM) extends his left hand outward and marginal contact occurs with Davis' (SAC) right leg during the jump shot attempt.
King (SAC) commits a take foul on Winslow (MEM).

Davis (SAC) extends his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Porter's (MEM) left arm as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound. King (SAC) has his hand rested on Porter's front as the rebound falls overhead and marginal contact occurs.
Winslow (MEM) and Tillman (MEM) legally contest Davis' (SAC) shot attempt.
